    },
    "body": "In accordance with the proposal #1214 the default value of `TEMPLATES_AUTO_RELOAD` is set to `None` and by default templates will be reloaded only if the application is running in debug mode. A complete table of the various options:\n\n| `TEMPLATES_AUTO_RELOAD` | `DEBUG` | Templates auto reloaded? |\n| --- | --- | --- |\n| `None` | `False` | no |\n| `None` | `True` | yes |\n| `False` | `False` | no |\n| `False` | `True` | no |\n| `True` | `False` | yes |\n| `True` | `True` | yes |\n",
